window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Tis the season to be naughty....</i></b><br> <br> College hockey rivals turned lovers Jackson Reed and Killian Blackwell are about to face their toughest match yet: Christmas with both their families at the Reed mansion.<br> <br> Between sexual tension to melt the estate's ice sculptures, and a shared future that's anything but certain, this holiday season is bound to be unforgettable.<br> <br> The only question is whether the mansion—and their families—will survive their particular brand of Christmas spirit.<br> <br> <b>**This story features the couple from Brutal Titan and is an extension of their story. It is recommended to listen to Brutal Titan first.**</b></p>"; 
